  3.807372918659925*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"662c033c-a530-4bf6-b488-\
8f328d60da87"],

Cell["The purpose of this lesson is to...", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.807372921725031*^9, 
  3.807372939687728*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"de467749-c680-40e6-81e5-\
2f17434cc45b"],

Cell["\<\
prepare for the discussion of waves in quantum mechanics by introducing the \
concept of a classical wave and how we can describe it mathematically.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.807372959293992*^9, 3.807373032864848*^9}, {
   3.807373069698522*^9, 3.807373151188424*^9}, {3.807457129031746*^9, 
   3.807457179100905*^9}, {3.807458120036808*^9, 3.80745814208899*^9}, {
   3.807458614074108*^9, 3.8074586346848297`*^9}, {3.807617515606489*^9, 
   3.80761758683189*^9}, {3.8076305528346233`*^9, 3.8076306273962183`*^9}, {
   3.8076346828072977`*^9, 3.8076346865160336`*^9}, 3.807868708707306*^9, {
   3.9146653630186653`*^9, 
   3.9146653654048133`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"043e5c07-30a2-4d42-ad8b-\
8a0f5e1693e5"],

Cell["\<\
introduce some concepts that will occur repeatedly in quantum mechanics, such \
as separation of variables and quantization through boundary conditions.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.807372959293992*^9, 3.807373032864848*^9}, {
   3.807373069698522*^9, 3.807373151188424*^9}, {3.807457129031746*^9, 
   3.807457179100905*^9}, {3.807458120036808*^9, 3.80745814208899*^9}, {
   3.807458614074108*^9, 3.8074586346848297`*^9}, {3.807617515606489*^9, 
   3.80761758683189*^9}, {3.8076305528346233`*^9, 3.8076306273962183`*^9}, {
   3.8076346890590377`*^9, 3.807634717876937*^9}, 3.8078687114326825`*^9, {
   3.9146654785359726`*^9, 
   3.9146654785449705`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dd8baa80-8616-4848-a5e1-\
1f4d930dc256"],

Cell["\<\
present the time-independent Schr\[ODoubleDot]dinger equation through an \
analogy with the classical wave equation.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.807372959293992*^9, 3.807373032864848*^9}, {
   3.807373069698522*^9, 3.807373151188424*^9}, {3.807457129031746*^9, 
   3.807457179100905*^9}, {3.807458120036808*^9, 3.80745814208899*^9}, {
   3.807458614074108*^9, 3.8074586346848297`*^9}, {3.807617515606489*^9, 
   3.80761758683189*^9}, {3.8076305528346233`*^9, 3.8076306273962183`*^9}, {
   3.8076346890590377`*^9, 3.807634717876937*^9}, 3.8078687114326825`*^9, {
   3.9146654788988347`*^9, 
   3.914665509788892*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"26e575f3-dbd3-465e-9bb4-\
8a4cc163bc46"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "introduce the formalism for working in three-dimensional (",
 StyleBox["x",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", ",
 StyleBox["y",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", ",
 StyleBox["z ",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ") space."
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.807372959293992*^9, 3.807373032864848*^9}, {
   3.807373069698522*^9, 3.807373151188424*^9}, {3.807457129031746*^9, 
   3.807457179100905*^9}, {3.807458120036808*^9, 3.80745814208899*^9}, {
