   3.8076307277658367`*^9}, 3.8078687276987715`*^9, {3.9146655442117195`*^9, 
   3.9146655447641306`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"05221de9-1141-4188-abc5-\
0dd77c51d9bd"],

Cell["\<\
detail the relationship between quantization and boundary conditions.\
\>", "Item",
